<subSubSection pageId="2" pageNumber="45" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="2.[151,1437,805,2030]" pageId="2" pageNumber="45">
<emphasis box="[197,321,1153,1178]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="45">Etymology</emphasis>
. We name this new species in memory of Sir Edmund Hillary, the Patron of the 
<collectingCountry box="[1277,1436,1153,1179]" name="New Zealand" pageId="2" pageNumber="45">New Zealand</collectingCountry>
Native Forests Restoration Trust until his death in 
<date box="[762,926,1192,1218]" pageId="2" pageNumber="45" value="2008-01">
January 
<number box="[863,926,1192,1218]" pageId="2" pageNumber="45" value="2008.0">2008</number>
</date>
, and to honour the Trust´s dedicated work from which forest-dwelling arthropods, such as fungus gnats, should benefit greatly.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="2.[151,1437,805,2030]" pageId="2" pageNumber="45">
<typeStatus box="[197,261,1269,1294]" pageId="2" pageNumber="45">
<emphasis box="[197,261,1269,1294]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="45">Types</emphasis>
</typeStatus>
. 
<emphasis box="[278,385,1269,1294]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="45">
<typeStatus box="[278,385,1269,1294]" pageId="2" pageNumber="45">Holotype</typeStatus>
</emphasis>
. Male, 
<collectingCountry box="[477,637,1269,1295]" name="New Zealand" pageId="2" pageNumber="45">New Zealand</collectingCountry>
, South Island, Westland, Westland National Park, Canavan´s Knob, in grassy clearing in mixed podocarp forest, 
<quantity box="[668,745,1308,1334]" metricMagnitude="2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.4" pageId="2" pageNumber="45" unit="m" value="140.0">140 m</quantity>
, 
<date box="[756,944,1308,1334]" pageId="2" pageNumber="45" value="1982-10" valueMax="1982-11-31" valueMin="1982-10-00">
Oct.–Nov. 
<number box="[883,944,1308,1334]" pageId="2" pageNumber="45" value="1982.0">1982</number>
</date>
, by Malaise trap, A. B. Miller (in 
<collectionCode LSID="urn:lsid:biocol.org:col:34070" box="[1339,1424,1308,1334]" httpUri="http://biocol.org/urn:lsid:biocol.org:col:34070" name="New Zealand Arthropod Collection" pageId="2" pageNumber="45">NZAC</collectionCode>
). 
